data.description: Move in ready! Country living with NO HOA! Spacious living room, kitchen with lots of cabinet and counter space. Spacious bedrooms, Dual vanity in primary bath, stand up shower and soaking tub. All rooms have been freshly painted. Nice deck and back yard with carport and storage shed.  Metal roof installed in 2019, HVAC and well pump were replaced in 2020. Seller is offering a $1500 buyer credit at closing.
